Summary: This section lists the properties available for configuring an EditorDock.

* available_layouts (bitfield[DockLayout]): The available_layouts property. Default: 5
* closable (bool): The closable property. Default: false
* default_slot (DockSlot): The default_slot property. Default: -1
* dock_icon (Texture2D): The dock_icon property.
* dock_shortcut (Shortcut): The dock_shortcut property.
* force_show_icon (bool): The force_show_icon property. Default: false
* global (bool): The global property. Default: true
* icon_name (StringName): The icon_name property. Default: &""
* layout_key (String): The layout_key property. Default: ""
* title (String): The title property. Default: ""
* title_color (Color): The title_color property. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 0)
* transient (bool): The transient property. Default: false
